@baseUrl = http://localhost:5283

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Add Hurda item — Yeni eşya ekle (Admin)
# Token'ı login yanıtından yapıştırın.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hurda/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_JWT

{
  "name": "Örnek malzeme",
  "description": "Kod: 0008002 | Kalıp: C000007391 | Cavity: A-B",
  "scrapAmount": 0
}

### Update Hurda Item (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/hurda/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_JWT

{
  "scrapAmount": 10
}